## Why This Direction

The deterministic metrics module reached feature-complete status (sessions 12-19, all 9/10). Reviewer and self-reflection both pointed to LLM-as-judge as the next high-value direction. The proposal specifies 5 dimensions but only 2 were implemented — this was the clearest gap.

## Next Steps

- Multi-judge ensemble (2-3 judges, majority vote) — proposal section 3.3
- CLI `--no-randomize` flag for reproducible evaluation
- End-to-end test with real trace demonstrating all 5 dimensions
